with no friends at all.

01:13:04.505 --> 01:13:07.384
I don't need friends. I'm my own man.

01:13:10.136 --> 01:13:11.888
Just like Liberace.

01:13:29.989 --> 01:13:31.366
Christopher.

01:13:31.991 --> 01:13:34.335
