01:15:43.039 --> 01:15:44.541
It's yours...

01:15:46.417 --> 01:15:48.215
Under one condition.

01:15:51.297 --> 01:15:54.301
Stay away from Mary for good.

01:16:02.892 --> 01:16:05.111
Give this to Isaac from me.

01:16:14.236 --> 01:16:15.533
