01:18:02.970 --> 01:18:05.064
You promise? Only five minutes.

01:18:05.222 --> 01:18:07.520
- Mary, please!
- Don't worry.

01:18:07.933 --> 01:18:09.185
Oh, God!

01:18:21.071 --> 01:18:23.870
