01:22:01.083 --> 01:22:02.960
Okay, then I hate you.

01:22:10.342 --> 01:22:11.844
No, you don't.

01:22:13.303 --> 01:22:14.976
Then I love you.

01:22:17.599 --> 01:22:18.976
Define love.

01:23:10.486 --> 01:23:12.534
